---
// CTA Section for TieBack
---

<section id="cta" class="py-32 bg-white border-t border-slate-100" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c1">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c3">
    <div class="reveal reveal-scale" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c4">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c5">Ready for what's coming.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c6">
        The Digital Product Passport is only the beginning. Product identity, ownership, and verification will define how brands operate in the next decade.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c7">
        <a href="/request-access" class="px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-medium bg-blue-700 text-white hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all shadow-sm" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:c8">
          Request Access
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-8" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:cohort">
        Access is released in carefully selected cohorts.
      </p>

      {/* Original Hero Image moved to bottom */}
      <div class="mt-20 relative mx-auto max-w-4xl group" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:hero-swap">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-[2rem] blur opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition duration-1000" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:qxj7fa"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 bg-white p-2 shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:qxj7f7">
          <img 
            crossorigin="anonymous"
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" 
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1684610527413-66eec7828690?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
            sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 80vw"
            alt="TieBack AI Network Visualization" 
            class="w-full h-auto aspect-video object-cover rounded-[1.5rem]" data-ps="src/components/home/CTA.astro:2xpr82" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
